{
  "video_id": "8_zk2DpgLCs",
  "title": "3 things I learned while my plane crashed | Ric Elias",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 14000.0,
      "text": "翻訳: Satoshi Tatsuhara 校正: Takako Sato"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15000.0,
      "end_time": 18000.0,
      "text": "Imagine a big explosion"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18000.0,
      "end_time": 21000.0,
      "text": "as you climb through 3,000 ft."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21000.0,
      "end_time": 25000.0,
      "text": "Imagine a plane full of smoke."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25000.0,
      "end_time": 27000.0,
      "text": "Imagine an engine going clack, clack, clack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27000.0,
      "end_time": 29000.0,
      "text": "clack, clack, clack, clack."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29000.0,
      "end_time": 31000.0,
      "text": "It sounds scary."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31000.0,
      "end_time": 34000.0,
      "text": "Well I had a unique seat that day. I was sitting in 1D."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34000.0,
      "end_time": 37000.0,
      "text": "I was the only one who could talk to the flight attendants."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37000.0,
      "end_time": 39000.0,
      "text": "So I looked at them right away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39000.0,
      "end_time": 42000.0,
      "text": "and they said, \"No problem. We probably hit some birds.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42000.0,
      "end_time": 44000.0,
      "text": "The pilot had already turned the plane around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44000.0,
      "end_time": 46000.0,
      "text": "and we weren't that far."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46000.0,
      "end_time": 48000.0,
      "text": "You could see Manhattan."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48000.0,
      "end_time": 50000.0,
      "text": "Two minutes later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50000.0,
      "end_time": 53000.0,
      "text": "three things happened at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53000.0,
      "end_time": 57000.0,
      "text": "The pilot lines up  the plane with the Hudson River."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57000.0,
      "end_time": 59000.0,
      "text": "That's usually not the route."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59000.0,
      "end_time": 61000.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61000.0,
      "end_time": 64000.0,
      "text": "He turns off the engines."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64000.0,
      "end_time": 67000.0,
      "text": "Now imagine being in a plane with no sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67000.0,
      "end_time": 69000.0,
      "text": "And then he says three words --"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69000.0,
      "end_time": 72000.0,
      "text": "the most unemotional three words I've ever heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72000.0,
      "end_time": 75000.0,
      "text": "He says, \"brace for impact .\""
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76000.0,
      "end_time": 78000.0,
      "text": "I didn't have to talk to the flight attendant anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78000.0,
      "end_time": 81000.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81000.0,
      "end_time": 83000.0,
      "text": "I could see in her eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83000.0,
      "end_time": 86000.0,
      "text": "it was terror. Life was over."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86000.0,
      "end_time": 89000.0,
      "text": "Now I want to share with you three things I learned about myself that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91000.0,
      "end_time": 94000.0,
      "text": "I learned that it all changes in an instant."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94000.0,
      "end_time": 96000.0,
      "text": "We have this bucket list,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96000.0,
      "end_time": 98000.0,
      "text": "we have these things we want to do in life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98000.0,
      "end_time": 101000.0,
      "text": "and I thought about all the people I wanted to reach out to that I didn't,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101000.0,
      "end_time": 104000.0,
      "text": "all the fences I wanted to mend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104000.0,
      "end_time": 107000.0,
      "text": "all the experiences I wanted to have and I never did."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107000.0,
      "end_time": 110000.0,
      "text": "As I thought about that later on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110000.0,
      "end_time": 112000.0,
      "text": "I came up with a saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 112000.0,
      "end_time": 115000.0,
      "text": "which is, \"I collect bad wines.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115000.0,
      "end_time": 118000.0,
      "text": "Because if the wine is ready and the person is there, I'm opening it."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118000.0,
      "end_time": 121000.0,
      "text": "I no longer want to postpone anything in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121000.0,
      "end_time": 123000.0,
      "text": "And that urgency, that purpose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 123000.0,
      "end_time": 126000.0,
      "text": "has really changed my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126000.0,
      "end_time": 128000.0,
      "text": "The second thing I learned that day --"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128000.0,
      "end_time": 131000.0,
      "text": "and this is as we clear the George Washington Bridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131000.0,
      "end_time": 134000.0,
      "text": "which was by not a lot --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134000.0,
      "end_time": 136000.0,
      "text": "I thought about, wow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136000.0,
      "end_time": 138000.0,
      "text": "I really feel one real regret."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138000.0,
      "end_time": 140000.0,
      "text": "I've lived a good life."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140000.0,
      "end_time": 142000.0,
      "text": "In my own humanity and mistakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142000.0,
      "end_time": 144000.0,
      "text": "I've tried to get better at everything I tried."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144000.0,
      "end_time": 146000.0,
      "text": "But in my humanity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 146000.0,
      "end_time": 148000.0,
      "text": "I also allow my ego to get in."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 148000.0,
      "end_time": 151000.0,
      "text": "And I regretted the time I wasted"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 151000.0,
      "end_time": 153000.0,
      "text": "on things that did not matter"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 153000.0,
      "end_time": 155000.0,
      "text": "with people that matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 155000.0,
      "end_time": 158000.0,
      "text": "And I thought about my relationship with my wife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 158000.0,
      "end_time": 160000.0,
      "text": "with my friends, with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 160000.0,
      "end_time": 162000.0,
      "text": "And after, as I reflected on that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 162000.0,
      "end_time": 165000.0,
      "text": "I decided to eliminate  negative energy from my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 165000.0,
      "end_time": 167000.0,
      "text": "It's not perfect, but it's a lot better."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 167000.0,
      "end_time": 169000.0,
      "text": "I've not had a fight with my wife in two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 169000.0,
      "end_time": 171000.0,
      "text": "It feels great."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 171000.0,
      "end_time": 173000.0,
      "text": "I no longer try to be right;"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 173000.0,
      "end_time": 176000.0,
      "text": "I choose to be happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 176000.0,
      "end_time": 178000.0,
      "text": "The third thing I learned --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178000.0,
      "end_time": 180000.0,
      "text": "and this is as your mental clock"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 180000.0,
      "end_time": 182000.0,
      "text": "starts going, \"15, 14, 13.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 182000.0,
      "end_time": 184000.0,
      "text": "You can see the water coming."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 184000.0,
      "end_time": 186000.0,
      "text": "I'm saying, \"Please blow up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 186000.0,
      "end_time": 188000.0,
      "text": "I don't want this thing to break in 20 pieces"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 188000.0,
      "end_time": 191000.0,
      "text": "like you've seen in those documentaries."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 191000.0,
      "end_time": 193000.0,
      "text": "And as we're coming down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 193000.0,
      "end_time": 195000.0,
      "text": "I had a sense of, wow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 195000.0,
      "end_time": 198000.0,
      "text": "dying is not scary."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 198000.0,
      "end_time": 201000.0,
      "text": "It's almost like we've been preparing for it our whole lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 201000.0,
      "end_time": 203000.0,
      "text": "But it was very sad."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 203000.0,
      "end_time": 206000.0,
      "text": "I didn't want to go; I love my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 206000.0,
      "end_time": 208000.0,
      "text": "And that sadness"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 208000.0,
      "end_time": 210000.0,
      "text": "really framed in one thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 210000.0,
      "end_time": 213000.0,
      "text": "which is, I only wish for one thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 213000.0,
      "end_time": 217000.0,
      "text": "I only wish I could see my kids grow up."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 217000.0,
      "end_time": 220000.0,
      "text": "About a month later, I was at a performance by my daughter --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 220000.0,
      "end_time": 223000.0,
      "text": "first-grader, not much artistic talent ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 223000.0,
      "end_time": 225000.0,
      "text": "... yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 225000.0,
      "end_time": 227000.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 227000.0,
      "end_time": 232000.0,
      "text": "And I'm bawling , I'm crying, like a little kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 232000.0,
      "end_time": 235000.0,
      "text": "And it made all the sense in the world to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 235000.0,
      "end_time": 237000.0,
      "text": "I realized at that point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 237000.0,
      "end_time": 239000.0,
      "text": "by connecting those two dots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 239000.0,
      "end_time": 241000.0,
      "text": "that the only thing that matters in my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 241000.0,
      "end_time": 243000.0,
      "text": "is being a great dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 243000.0,
      "end_time": 246000.0,
      "text": "Above all, above all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 246000.0,
      "end_time": 248000.0,
      "text": "the only goal I have in life"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 248000.0,
      "end_time": 250000.0,
      "text": "is to be a good dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 250000.0,
      "end_time": 252000.0,
      "text": "I was given the gift of a miracle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 252000.0,
      "end_time": 254000.0,
      "text": "of not dying that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 254000.0,
      "end_time": 256000.0,
      "text": "I was given another gift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 256000.0,
      "end_time": 258000.0,
      "text": "which was to be able to see into the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 258000.0,
      "end_time": 260000.0,
      "text": "and come back"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 260000.0,
      "end_time": 262000.0,
      "text": "and live differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 262000.0,
      "end_time": 265000.0,
      "text": "I challenge you guys that are flying today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 265000.0,
      "end_time": 268000.0,
      "text": "imagine the same thing happens on your plane --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 268000.0,
      "end_time": 270000.0,
      "text": "and please don't --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 270000.0,
      "end_time": 272000.0,
      "text": "but imagine, and how would you change?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 272000.0,
      "end_time": 275000.0,
      "text": "What would you get done that you're waiting to get done"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 275000.0,
      "end_time": 277000.0,
      "text": "because you think you'll be here forever?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 277000.0,
      "end_time": 279000.0,
      "text": "How would you change your relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 279000.0,
      "end_time": 281000.0,
      "text": "and the negative energy in them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 281000.0,
      "end_time": 284000.0,
      "text": "And more than anything, are you being the best parent you can?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 284000.0,
      "end_time": 286000.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 286000.0,
      "end_time": 296000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}